reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Looks good but the bracelet is almost made for a child
reviews.reviewText: My wife got this for a family photo. She doesn’t have large wrists at all, and had a hard time getting the bracelet on. It looked too small so she went with just the earrings and necklace. She loves how it looks but was disappointed with how tightly the bracelet fit.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This acrylic set is a winner!
reviews.reviewText: Beautiful, unique & so affordable. A colorful pastel-primary blend of acrylic jewelry that will take your outfit to the next level! The pieces are large, but not overly so...meaning they do not detract from an outfit, but rather add a tasteful yet fun element.I agree with other reviews that the bracelet opening is very narrow & unforgiving (& I'm small framed). ***The bracelet would be difficult to put on if you are big boned.***Would make a fantastic gift. Very impressed with this purchase!
